text: On Januarius monðe, gyf hit þunreð, hit bodeð toweard mycele windes, & wel gewænde eorðe wæstme, & gefiht.
On Februarius monðe, gyf hit þunreð, hit bodeð manegra manna cwealm, & mæst þære ricen.
On Mærces monðe, hit bodeð mycele windes, & wæstmes wel gewænde, & folc unsehte.
On April, hit bodeð blisful gear, & yfelre manna deað.
On Mai, hit bodeð hunger gear.
On Junius monðe, hit bodeð mycele windes, & wulfene wodnysse, & leona.
On Julius monðe, hit bodeð wæstme wel gewænde, & oref forfærð.
On Hærfest, hit bodeð god gear, & mæn sicelið.
On Setembre, hit bodeð god gear, <ac> riccere manna slege.
On Octobre, hit bodeð mycelne wind & wæstme toweard & treowena wæstme gæsne.
On Nouembre, hit bodeð blisfull gear, & wæstme toweard.
On Decembre, hit bodeð god gear on tilðe, & sibb, & sehte.
